channel.title: NRS3server v2 BETA (released)
channel.description:
[center][img]http://i45.tinypic.com/2466li9.gif[/img] This is the V2 everyone has been waiting to see i will keep a full out update list to make sure your up with our features and updates so far below recent updates is what we have accomplished
[size=10pt][img]http://i.imgur.com/1klA6.png[/img][url=http://nrs3server.info]HomePage[/url] [img]http://i44.tinypic.com/9j41t1.jpg[/img][url=http://rs3server.freesmfhosting.com]Forums[/url] [img]http://i56.tinypic.com/imijbl.png[/img][url=http://nrs3server.info/webclient.html]Play Now[/url][/size]
Here are some features
[size=14pt][b][u]Recent Updates:[/u][/b][/size] - Grand exchange buying only - QBD 100% - Polypore Dungeon - Dungeoneering 100% - 1 npc for all weapons and armours - all pets - Dragonbone - Flaming Skulls - 725 cache - Anti lagg system - vote4cash - much more etc..
[size=12pt][u][b]Features:[/b][/u][/size] - Switching is near perfect - All Spellbooks are accessible via Commands and altars - Storm of Armadyl, New boots, and more. - Armours such as Torva, Barrows, and PvP Armour Degrade when in use and when they are dropped in PvP - Auras are all complete except for Salvation and Corruption bonuses work wings are glitched
(Bosses) - King Black Dragon with all attacks and effects - Tormented Demons with all 3 switches - Full Nex with all 4 stages (Flawless) - 85% Godwars - Corporeal beast with Impact hits and all correct attacks - Frost dragons - Dominion Tower - Barrows{prizes glitchy still} & More...
Pvp/PK/PVM/Combat - Near Perfect combat, 99.9% flawless - Switching better than RS - Full Summoning!! - Armour set effects all added! - Degrading Pvp Armours - Storm Of Armadyl Spell - Flawless Prayer system (Normal/Ancient Prayers/Lunar)
Random Stuff: - All special attacks working properly for Most Weapons! - Quick Chat 100% - music everyone knows that - custom maps - donorzones staffzones and more
Armours/Bosses: - All new 711 armours obv we all know - Bosses are upgraded to new looks - Jad waves maxed out to 65 - Armours are almost all update to date with bonuses and stats - Each armour that need requirements on RS is same on here now - Quests are partially made
Polypore Dungeon [IMG]http://i45.tinypic.com/30j4v0p.png[/img] Grand Exchange There is no red green or yellow colors the action is instant so there is no waiting time until i get more players then i will base it more on eco [IMG]http://i49.tinypic.com/j12h40.png[/img] Dungeoneering [IMG]http://i48.tinypic.com/3133e2t.png[/img] Queen Black Dragon [IMG]http://i45.tinypic.com/4rpc42.png[/img] Flaming Skulls (this picture everyone loves to see so i put in for fun) [IMG]http://i49.tinypic.com/2q01xnc.png[/img] Emotes for loyalty points [IMG]http://i47.tinypic.com/huj5sg.png[/img]
Much more to come
Our team TimeRS3 Neroxx
[center]
